'''美國聯合衛理公會''' （United Methodist Church，UMC），[[循道宗|循道宗]]教會之一，[[教會體制|教會體制]]採修訂過的[[主教制|主教制]]（{{tsl|en|Connexionalism|Connexionalism}}），是[[美國|美國]][[主流新教|主流新教]]（Oldline Protestant）的教會之一，也是美國最大型的[[循道宗|循道宗]]教會<ref>{{cite news|title=The 15 Largest Protestant Denominations in the United States|url=https://www.christianpost.com/news/the-15-largest-protestant-denominations-in-the-united-states-92731/|agency=christian post|accessdate=2017-11-16|archive-date=2017-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171114093504/https://www.christianpost.com/news/the-15-largest-protestant-denominations-in-the-united-states-92731/|dead-url=no}} I recently gleaned the top 15 denominations by membership in the United States from their reports：
# Southern Baptist Convention: 16.2 million members
# The United Methodist Church: 7.8 million members</ref>。2014年，教會有3,668,034人受洗的教友 <ref name="elca stats">{{cite web|url=http://www.elca.org/News-and-Events/ELCA-Facts|title=ELCA Facts|work=ELCA.org|accessdate=2017-11-16|archive-date=2017-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171121224817/http://www.elca.org/News-and-Events/ELCA-Facts|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

UMC的神學觀源自[[衛斯理主義|衛斯理主義]]的{{tsl|en|Christian revival|復興運動 (基督教)|復興運動}}，採[[阿民念主義|阿民念主義]]的立場，並著重受到[[聖靈|聖靈]]感動的經驗，接受{{tsl|en|Articles of Religion (Methodist)|信仰要道}}、{{tsl|en|Confession of Faith (United Methodist)|認信文 (循道宗)|認信文}}、衛理會組織章程，以及[[約翰·衛斯理|約翰·衛斯理]]的佈道集和他對新約的解釋筆記。這些教義準則受其憲章的保護，而幾乎不可更動<ref>{{cite web|title=Doctrinal Standards in The United Methodist Church|url=http://www.umc.org/what-we-believe/doctrinal-standards-in-the-united-methodist-church|accessdate=2017-11-16|archive-date=2018-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180125131412/http://www.umc.org/what-we-believe/doctrinal-standards-in-the-united-methodist-church|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

按照[[循道宗|循道宗]]解釋教義和律法的{{tsl|en|Book of Discipline (United Methodist)|紀律書}}描述，衛理會的神學是「普世的、福音的，以及改革的」（catholic, evangelical, and reformed）。按照{{tsl|en|Wesleyan Quadrilateral|衛斯理神學四支柱}}，UMC的神學強調[[理性|理性]]、基督教傳統、([[重生_(基督教)|重生]])經驗共同對聖經的詮釋作用。

UMC參與[[普世教會協會|普世教會協會]]以及{{tsl|en|World Methodist Council|世界循道衛理宗協會}}，並和[[美國福音路德教會|美國福音路德教會]]達成[[共融|共融]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Full Communion Partners|url=https://www.elca.org/Faith/Ecumenical-and-Inter-Religious-Relations/Full-Communion|website=Evangelical Lutheran Church in America|accessdate=2017-11-16|archive-date=2017-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116193008/http://www.elca.org/Faith/Ecumenical-and-Inter-Religious-Relations/Full-Communion|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，UMC尋求成為[[世界福音聯盟|世界福音聯盟]]觀察員的機會<ref name="Thomas C. Oden—NAE">{{cite book|url = https://books.google.com/books?id=pB6BrgQRjbQC&pg=PA143&dq=Taskforce+of+United+Methodists+on+Abortion+and+Sexuality&cd=2#v=onepage&q=Taskforce%20of%20United%20Methodists%20on%20Abortion%20and%20Sexuality&f=false|title = The rebirth of orthodoxy: signs of new life in Christianity|quote = For the first time, the United Methodist Church voted to seek observer status in the National Association of Evangelicals and the World Evangelical Fellowship.|publisher = [[HarperCollins|HarperCollins]]|accessdate = June 8, 2007|archive-date = 2016-05-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160519134021/https://books.google.com/books?id=pB6BrgQRjbQC&pg=PA143&dq=Taskforce+of+United+Methodists+on+Abortion+and+Sexuality&cd=2#v=onepage&q=Taskforce%20of%20United%20Methodists%20on%20Abortion%20and%20Sexuality&f=false|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

在2006年，{{tsl|en|World Methodist Council|世界循道衛理宗協會}}投票決定採納《[[關於稱義教義的聯合聲明|關於稱義教義的聯合聲明]]》，該聯合聲明由{{tsl|en|Lutheran World Federation|世界信義宗聯會}}和[[羅馬天主教會|羅馬天主教會]]在1999年發表，宣稱雙方教會對「通過對基督的信念，憑藉[[基督教的神|神]]的恩典稱義」這一觀點的一致<ref name="UMC—World Methodists approve further ecumenical dialogue">{{cite web|url = http://www.umc.org/site/c.gjJTJbMUIuE/b.1863123/k.FF49/World_Methodists_approve_further_ecumenical_dialogue.htm|title = World Methodists approve further ecumenical dialogue|publisher = The United Methodist Church|accessdate = June 8, 2007|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060721210415/http://www.umc.org/site/c.gjJTJbMUIuE/b.1863123/k.FF49/World_Methodists_approve_further_ecumenical_dialogue.htm|archive-date = 2006-07-21|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

美國聯合衛理公會幾乎每一州設立一年議會甚至多個年議會，每個年議會由會督主持。總議會四年舉行一次會議，由會督團主持（會督團遴選一位擔任主席）

== 歷史==
[[衛理會|衛理會]]原為[[聖公會|聖公會]]內的一派，後逐漸獨立。[[美國獨立|美國獨立]]後，美國衛斯理宗脫離聖公會而組成獨立的教會。其後教會分裂為美以美會、監理會、美普會、循理會和聖教會等。於1939年，美以美會、監理會和美普會合併成美國衛理公會。

聯合衞理公會成立於1968年，由美國衞理公會和福音[[同寅會|同寅會]]合併而成。現在聯合衞理教會是世界最大的循道宗教會，全世界有教友約1210萬人。

